      <memberdef kind="function" id="namespaceSimGateway_1aa708bae3840992ba113450b98dc0dc68" prot="public" static="no" const="no" explicit="no" inline="no" virt="non-virtual">
        <type>void</type>
        <definition>void SimGateway::setup</definition>
        <argsstring>(SerialUART &amp;uart, uint8_t txPin=DEFAULT_UART_TX_PIN, uint8_t rxPin=DEFAULT_UART_RX_PIN)</argsstring>
        <name>setup</name>
        <qualifiedname>SimGateway::setup</qualifiedname>
        <param>
          <type>SerialUART &amp;</type>
          <declname>uart</declname>
        </param>
        <param>
          <type>uint8_t</type>
          <declname>txPin</declname>
          <defval>DEFAULT_UART_TX_PIN</defval>
        </param>
        <param>
          <type>uint8_t</type>
          <declname>rxPin</declname>
          <defval>DEFAULT_UART_RX_PIN</defval>
        </param>
        <briefdescription>
<para>Initialise USB identity, OpenSkyhawkJoystick, and UART link to <ref refid="namespacePanelBridge" kindref="compound">PanelBridge</ref>. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>Must be the first call in the sketch&apos;s <ref refid="namespaceSimGateway_1aa708bae3840992ba113450b98dc0dc68" kindref="member">setup()</ref>. Sets USB identity before the TinyUSB stack enumerates:<itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>Manufacturer: &quot;OpenSkyhawk&quot;</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Product: &quot;A-4E Skyhawk&quot;</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>VID/PID: 0x2E8A / 0x4134</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>CDC port: &quot;A-4E Skyhawk DCS-BIOS&quot; (iInterface — names the serial port) Configures the UART pins and calls uart.begin(250000), then calls OsJoystick.begin() to initialise the HID descriptor and enumerate.</para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
<para><parameterlist kind="param"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>uart</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>Hardware UART connected to <ref refid="namespacePanelBridge" kindref="compound">PanelBridge</ref> (Serial1 / UART0 on standard board). </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>txPin</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>RP2040 UART TX pin. Defaults to GP0, wired to STM32 PA3. </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>rxPin</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>RP2040 UART RX pin. Defaults to GP1, wired to STM32 PA2. </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
</parameterlist>
</para>
        </detaileddescription>
        <inbodydescription>
        </inbodydescription>
        <location file="Firmware/Libraries/SimGateway/SimGateway.cpp" line="436" column="6" bodyfile="Firmware/Libraries/SimGateway/SimGateway.cpp" bodystart="436" bodyend="465" declfile="Firmware/Libraries/SimGateway/SimGateway.h" declline="148" declcolumn="6"/>
